## Description {#details}

Generic IR <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/platform">Platform</a> Support.

Scrapes llvm.global&#95;ctors and llvm.global&#95;dtors and replaces them with specially named &#39;init&#39; and &#39;deinit&#39;. Injects definitions / interposes for some runtime API, including &#95;&#95;cxa&#95;atexit, dlopen, and dlclose.

Definition at line 133 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/lib/lib/executionengine/lib/executionengine/orc/lljit-cpp">LLJIT.cpp</a>.
